Mycelium is an agent skill, not a standalone tool. The skill
teaches any agent the convention on-demand: read notes on arrival,
write notes on departure. The description triggers on 'working in
a git repo' which is nearly always. This means adoption is zero-cost —
no install, no setup, just load the skill and start using git notes.
